banner.description: I consider myself passionate about technology and constantly learning. I am currently a Full Stack web developer. I have worked on several personal projects using technologies such as Java, JavaScript, React, Node.js, Express and SQL   I am a proactive, focused, enthusiastic person and I like to work as part of a team. My focus is on constant learning and the search for the best techniques and good practices. I am constantly looking for opportunities to expand my knowledge.
